runLine() - Method in class fi.hu.cs.titokone.Processor
Process next instruction, Processing Cycle of an instruction: 1. mar = pc 2. mbr = RAM(pc) 3. ir = mbr 4. analyze binaryCommand, if ok, call method of the current operation type: 112 SVC 51-54 Stack operations: push, pop, pushr, popr 50 EXIT 49 CALL 32-44 Branching operations (set GEL-bits) 31 Comp 17-30 ALU operations 1-4 Data transfer (LOAD, STORE, IN, OUT) 0 NOP, do nothing 5. check addressing mode -->mar = address -->mbr = get value 6. tr = mbr if(112) --> SVC if(51-54) --> Stack if(49-50) --> Subroutine if(32-44) --> Branch if(17-31) --> ALU if(1-4) --> Transfer
